overview: Naylor's back and on this edition he sits down with the one and only, Karlee Perez. You may know her as Catrina on Lucha Underground or from her days in NXT as Maxine.  Karlee and Naylor dish about their time in developmental, working under the tutelage, if you will, of Dusty Rhodes and then they dive into all things Lucha! The pair go in depth on the awesomeness that is Lucha Underground!
title: Hitting The Highspots - Karlee Perez
